# Test Scenarios for Graduation Check API

This document provides JSON payloads to test various course conditions (prerequisites, corequisites, etc.) using the API endpoint:

**Endpoint:** `POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/graduation/check/name`

**Curriculum Used:** `เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566` (from CSV)
**Admission Year:** `2566`

## 1. Simple Prerequisite Check
**Course:** [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362) (Computer and Programming Laboratory)
**Prerequisite:** `2301170` (Computer and Programming)

### Scenario: Missing Prerequisite (Fail)
Trying to take [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362) without `2301170`.

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 1
    }
  ]
}
```
**Expected Result:** `prerequisite_violations` should contain [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362) missing `2301170`.

### Scenario: Prerequisite Met (Pass)
Taking `2301170` before [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362).

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301170",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 3,
      "grade": "A"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 1
    }
  ]
}
```

## 2. OR Logic Prerequisite
**Course:** [2301180](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#49-99) (Exploring Computer Science)
**Prerequisite:** `2301170` OR `2301173`

### Scenario: Missing Both Options (Fail)
Taking [2301180](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#49-99) without `2301170` or `2301173`.

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301180",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 2
    }
  ]
}
```

### Scenario: One Option Met (Pass)
Taking `2301173` before [2301180](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#49-99).

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301173",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 4,
      "grade": "B"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301180",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 2
    }
  ]
}
```

## 3. AND Logic Prerequisite
**Course:** `2301261` (Introduction to Information Systems)
**Prerequisite:** `2301170` AND [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362)

### Scenario: Missing One Prerequisite (Fail)
Taking `2301261` with only `2301170`.

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301170",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 3,
      "grade": "C"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301261",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 3
    }
  ]
}
```

## 4. Complex Logic (AND + OR)
**Course:** `2301260` (Programming Techniques)
**Prerequisite:** [(2301170 AND 2301172) OR 2301173](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/internal/model/graduation.go#63-64)

### Scenario: Satisfying the AND Group (Pass)
Taking `2301170` and [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362).

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301170",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 3,
      "grade": "C"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 1,
      "grade": "B"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301260",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 4
    }
  ]
}
```

### Scenario: Satisfying the OR Option (Pass)
Taking `2301173` only.

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301173",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 4,
      "grade": "A"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301260",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 4
    }
  ]
}
```

## 5. Corequisite Check
**Course:** [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362) (Lab)
**Corequisite:** `2301170` (Lecture) - *Note: CSV says coreq is 2301170*

### Scenario: Taking Corequisite in Same Term (Pass)

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301170",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 3,
      "grade": "C"
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 1,
      "grade": "B"
    }
  ]
}
```

### Scenario: Taking Corequisite in Different Term (Fail)
*Note: Corequisites usually imply "must take together OR have passed previously". If passed previously, it's fine. If taking now, must be same term.*

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301170",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 3,
      "grade": "F" 
    },
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 2,
      "credits": 1
    }
  ]
}
```
*If 2301170 was F, it's not passed. If taking 2301172 in Sem 2, must take 2301170 in Sem 2 as well.*

## 6. Cross-Curriculum Check
The system automatically handles cross-curriculum checks by matching [Code](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/internal/handler/course_handler.go#54-76) and [Year](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/mocks.go#41-45).
If you take a course that is defined in another curriculum but shares the same Code and Year, it will be validated correctly.

## 7. C.F. Exemption
**Course:** [2301172](file:///Users/get/Documents/coding/checkjop-be/tests/graduation_service_test.go#325-362)
**Prerequisite:** `2301170`

### Scenario: Missing Prereq but Exempted (Pass)

```json
{
  "name_th": "เอกเดี่ยว-ฝึกงาน-2566",
  "admission_year": 2566,
  "courses": [
    {
      "course_code": "2301172",
      "year": 2566,
      "semester": 1,
      "credits": 1
    }
  ],
  "exemptions": ["2301172"]
}
```
*Note: Exemption usually applies to the course being taken (allowing it despite missing prereqs).*
